{"tid":1651746,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"整頓連登，由你我做起。","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T12:55:39.000Z","uid":307415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86d4c8de51bf10dd20894a90e23cddc61ab1e890","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n針對真心放負嘅手足</span></ins></span><br />\n呢排見到連登好多晦氣post。放個晦氣唔係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係唔該大家見到啲乜嘢手足做得唔好，對前景唔樂觀乜乜柒柒嘅，唔該提埋建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地而家要嘅係戰術行動post，連登唔撚係你地放負嘅平台，要放負唔該去whatsapp ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇諗過當熱門全部都係負能量嘅post，會對成個運動有幾大影響？話要贏話要清算警隊話要煲底見，然後喺到放負話冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你冇撚病呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比著我上嚟睇連登見到一堆咁嘅垃圾po，我都冇心機出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>針對五毛，警狗嘅處理方法</ins></span></span><br />\n如果大家睇完個po或者username知道係以上身份嚟嘅，請咁樣留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此人為(五毛/sir)，手足請封鎖負皮上一頁<br />\n然後不推文回覆。如果見到有人留言嘅話，請直接負皮上一頁，無論佢up乜都唔好覆!<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我再重申一次，條友無論up乜都唔好覆!!!</span></span>如果有人仲喺到覆佢嘅話手足麻煩redirect呢個post提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(當然要不推文)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>進階整頓手段</ins></span></span><br />\n當然呢啲只係個人建議，如果有更好嘅idea或者意見歡迎提出，大家一齊為連登出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><ins>1.設立放負區</ins></span></span><br />\n邊個開唔重要，我明白目前手足情緒起伏好大，咁點解唔開一個po做「垃圾桶」專門比你發洩呢？喺呢個post，你想講咩都得，放負隨便。其他人見到手足唔開心，即管去做情緒輔導師，幫助佢地平伏心情。放完負，發洩完去訓個覺，第二日精神曬，繼續去發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><ins>2.建立五毛user database</ins></span></span><br />\n對於每日都可以花幾粒鐘上連登嘅人嚟講，邊啲係五毛，邊啲係警狗，邊啲係真心膠心裡有數，但係對日日發夢嘅手足呢？淺黃呢？佢地點知？唔通真係佢地比人識破之後就見一個block一個咩，陣間啲仆街特登帶風向啲人冇意識到佢係五毛咪仆街？連登需要人去建立一個database，好似老豆搵仔咁記錄低五毛同埋mon post狗嘅id，做過嘅事等等，整合起嚟比大家block，咁樣佢地開po就根本帶唔到風向，因為個個都知佢地係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登有幾多ac啫，咪三十幾萬個，我睇下佢地有幾多殭屍帳號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁先"},{"pid":"d561cb988a48c6d8c2db4a52110fbc34c4c56119","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，大家幫推"},{"pid":"a3fd74e64c13c116662ec6a9ce115f69ecb15635","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"唔好對連登嘅現狀視若無睹，連登係淺黃，和理非收集資訊嘅渠道，係放大所有黑警罪證嘅最好平台。一日唔整頓好連登，我地一日都唔會贏，唔係講玩笑。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">整頓連登，由你我做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5db752c485920c91a7e94709fdf54eefd77ff195","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"d52f11c3b72d12fe4efc451d5673f613c3ce72e5","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"829041b8e57a274781cda9e7bfcbb9b819aa097c","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:39:10.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"9210a7c31cdaf99ce8047626cadef92a18c9b54c","tid":1651746,"uid":307415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"e1aeb5d18